This Web Technology Mini Project showcases that website provides the user to purchase 
games and gaming products. The website provides a login page, catalogue of items and 
search bar for the user to use the website and purchase items. 
The user can browse through the website for his desired item without logging in. For 
purchase, saving item to cart or creating a wish list the user has to login with his credentials.
Website provides the user a glimpse of the item through videos and images before 
purchasing the product. The product database will contain the productâ€™s name, images, 
videos, price, etc. and when a user creates an account their credentials are stored to the user 
database. Products can be searched from the search bar provided.
Admin can edit the catalogue through the product database to add or delete products and in 
user database admin can analyse the number of users logged in to the website.
